author: Jason Brennan
title: TV | Alan Carr: Chatty Man
text: The funnyman is joined by comedienne Sarah Millican, who talks about her new Outsider stand-up tour, and singer Alesha Dixon, who discusses her latest single, Tallest Woman. Gareth Malone also graces the sofa to speak about his new project The Naked Choir, while legendary musician Morrissey performs Kiss Me a Lot live in the studio. Not a bad lineup, not a bad lineup at all.
